  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.esoco.lib.property.HasId<java.lang.String>, de.esoco.lib.property.SingleSelection

    public class DeckPanel
extends SwitchPanel
    A panel that can contain multiple components of which only one is visible at a time like the cards in a deck of cards. The currently visible component can be set with the method SwitchPanel.setSelection(int). As the layout of a deck panel is defined by it's implementation setting a layout on an instance has no effect.
